{"tid":339502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲少女午夜跑步，被色魔騎險被姦","createTime":"2017-07-29T06:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T11:45:47.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d5c3c369127b876e4015531f69fb7cdc2f4f10","tid":339502,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"一名19歲女子，凌晨約2時行經秀茂坪順安道時，懷疑被一名約1.7米高男子從後箍頸，繼而非禮，男子其後逃去。警員接報到場調查，案件改列企圖強姦，交由秀茂坪警區重案組跟進調查，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，受害少女為一名熱愛跑步的學生，事發前她由順天邨出發跑步往觀塘APM商場一帶再折返，當他回家途中經過順天邨天韻樓時卻遇上色狼。色狼從後向她箍頸，將她㩒落地面，又用環保袋「笠頭」，騎在她身上企圖施暴，女事主不斷反抗呼叫，狂咬色狼手臂，疑色狼抵不住痛，又恐呼救聲驚動街坊，事敗逃去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170729&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57015546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170729%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57015546&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e340785f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170729%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57015546&h=53cf760b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170729&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57015546</a><br />\n【笠袋色魔】遭箍頸笠頭騎上身 19歲女保貞操「咬」退色魔"},{"pid":"7d9a0950f993367d485def6f18fe864956394598","tid":339502,"uid":22696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/142442_e90918af3e32f6b77da137a620e833a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F142442_e90918af3e32f6b77da137a620e833a8.jpg&h=8ffb4bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下個色狼係唔係入面先"},{"pid":"1cee7889034dc0747e7a7c30d0b0a788ad83a527","tid":339502,"uid":98317,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"跑步啲囡著到咁短......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\